Title: Tico-Tico no Fubá
Writer: Jacques Maret, Oswaldo Sampaio, Guilherme de Almeida
Actors: Anselmo Duarte, Tônia Carrero, Marisa Prado, Marina Freire
Plot: Fictionalized version of the life of Brazilian composer Zequinha de Abreu (1880-1935), who wrote the song "Tico-Tico no Fubá" that became an international hit in the 1940s.
